        <Parent_String>Gambier Islands [300021953], Polynesian [300021944], Oceanic [300021854], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
